OL,3,CNHS chair reflects on six years in the
OL,4,Cjob ahead of retirement
OL,6,FThe chair of an NHS Board has
OL,7,Freflected on her six years in the
OL,8,Frole, ahead of her retirement at the
OL,9,Fend of the month.
OL,11,FKaren Hamilton, Chair of NHS Borders,
OL,12,Fwas appointed in 2019, before which
OL,13,Fshe was a Non-Executive Director. Her
OL,14,Ftime in the lead role was dominated by
OL,15,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,17,FMs Hamilton told ITV Border: "To
OL,18,Fdescribe it as a rollercoaster is
OL,19,Fprobably an underestimation.
