OL,3,CNHS chair reflects on six years in the
OL,4,Cjob ahead of retirement
OL,6,FThe latest NHS Borders financial
OL,7,Freport from this year shows a deficit
OL,8,Fof #30million, but Ms Hamilton
OL,9,Fsuggests she has left the health board
OL,10,Fin a strong position.
OL,12,FShe said: "The work we are doing and
OL,13,Fthe advances that we're making in
OL,14,Fterms of trying to get ourselves back
OL,15,Fto financial balance, we're on the way.
OL,17,F"It's a long process. I'm talking
OL,18,Fyears, five years, probably... it's
OL,19,Fnot going to be an easy solution. And
OL,20,Fit's the same for pretty much all
OL,21,F(health) boards across Scotland.
