OL,3,CNHS chair reflects on six years in the
OL,4,Cjob ahead of retirement
OL,6,F"And then I figured out, actually,
OL,7,Fit's the way I do it which matters. I
OL,8,Fthink any new person coming into the
OL,9,Frole probably needs to do that and not
OL,10,Ftry to repeat what's been done in the
OL,11,Fpast."
OL,13,FMs Hamilton's successor as Chair of
OL,14,FNHS Borders has yet to be announced.
